N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 11.112 - Supervisory level qualifications

State Regulations
A supervising public health sanitarian must meet the qualifications for a public health sanitarian and have two years of experience as a public health sanitarian. Notes
